        <div class="heading_subtitle">What is Shivyog ?</div>
        <div class="dashed_divider"></div>
        <div class="heading_title">You life is in your hands</div>
        <p>hiv Yog defines God as the source of the infinite potential within every human being. Every human being has the potential to go beyond the limited identification with the body and mind. Shiv Yog provides us easy and practical ways to establish a connection with the infinite dimension from where everything in the manifest universe has been created. It is a scientific approach to living a 200% life – 100% worldly and 100% spiritual. It is a journey from Mindfulness to Inner Consciousness to Self-realization.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="shivyog_video_img"><a href="Javascript: void(0);" id="shivyog_impact_video_01" data-toggle="modal" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/d_U2fJzkSck" data-target="#myModal"><%= image_tag "v2/what_is_shivyog_video_01.jpg", class: "img-fluid img-no-border" %></a></div>
      </div>
