      <div class="dashed_divider"></div>
      <div class="heading_title_small">Dr. Avdhoot Shivanand has laid down three simple ways for a man to evolve from Nar to Narayan (from man to superman, from individual consciousness to cosmic consciousness), from finite to infinite.</div>
